	<section id="intro">

		<h1>Introduction</h1>
		<hr>

		<h4>When activated Mixture will automatically generate a sitemap based on the template directory for your project, <a href="http://quick.as/R6H4kr">view a screencast announcing this feature</a>.</h4>
		<p>All changes will be immediatley updated in the sitemap and <code>_sitemap.json</code> will be created in the "model" directory.</p>
		<p>When detected the sitemap data will be loaded and available from within the <code>mixture</code> model as <code>mixture.sitemap</code>. The sitemap will be in alphabetical order with the "Index" page at the top.</p>
